            "id": 6430013,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 華通(2313)股價殺至跌停，跌停價222.5元，成交78,221張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2313-TW</a>)23日10:08下跌24.5元，股價跌停報222.5元，委賣3,026張，成交78,221張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為多層印刷電路板。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2313-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌6.08%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.15%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-28,699 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-17,650 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-11,166 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+117 張</li> <li>融資增減：+4,830 張</li> <li>融券增減：+383 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
